        "timestamp": "2019-06-27 16:19:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nFollowing are the 2 changes required\n\n1) authorizeClient(..) method need following changes\n\nWhile deleting the topics, No need to check the Permission using APIKeys for topics created using the APIKeys and anonymous topics. You may use the operation (to conditionally add the else block)\n\n2) DMaaPResponseBuilder.respondOkWithHtml(..) and DMaaPResponseBuilder.respondOk(..) are replaced with the respondOk(. .). Enhance espondOk(. .) to support DMaaPResponseBuilder.respondOkWithHtml(..)",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
